  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of drug-eluting balloon angioplasty
      followed versus conventional balloon angioplasty in superficial femoral artery and popliteal
      artery re-stenosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
